data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Nestled in the heart of Orlando's sought-after North Goldenrod neighborhood, this delightful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom villa offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. Boasting a private carport and an array of desirable features, this property presents an ideal opportunity for those seeking a cozy retreat in a prime location. Low Maintenance Living: With a homeowner's association overseeing landscaping, you can enjoy a hassle-free lifestyle.  This property holds great potential for both homeowners and investors, with strong rental demand in this desirable area.  Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a piece of Orlando's thriving real estate market. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm of this wonderful villa for yourself.
